{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the manufacture and sale of plastic bottles",
        "additional_details": "In order to tackle this problem a ban is required.",
        "background": "We want the Government to take action to cut down plastic pollution by banning the manufacture and sale of plastic bottles, which make up a significant proportion of all plastic packaging.",
